	<h1>Look ahead with us:</h1>
	<p>BANK MEGA, is a high quality, customer centric and service driven Bank. Since inception in 2004, BANK MEGA has grown into a ‘Full Service Commercial Bank’ providing a complete range of products, services and technology driven digital offerings, catering to corporate, MSME & retail customers.BANK MEGA operates its Investment banking, Merchant banking & Brokerage businesses through MEGA SECURITIES and its Mutual Fund business through MEGA Asset Management (India) Limited, both wholly owned subsidiaries of the Bank. Headquartered in Mumbai, it has a pan-India presence across all 28 states and 9 Union Territories in India.</p>
    <h2>Learn how we’re supporting customers, employees and communities <br>in the pandemic and economic recovery:</h2>
	<p>BANK MEGA provides update on commitment to addressing economic inequities<br>This Bank created a new role teaching diverse youth about building wealth<br>BANK MEGA Altitude Connect reunites people with the faces and places they love<br>BANK MEGA launches industry-leading video banking options for customers.</p>
